348
00:26:46,160 --> 00:26:47,119
[SPEAKER_01] Da, počinju vas vikati.

349
00:26:47,200 --> 00:26:47,680
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo sam ja na Twitteru.

350
00:26:47,759 --> 00:26:49,359
[SPEAKER_01] Kad god ne gradim ono što trebam graditi, znam.

351
00:26:49,599 --> 00:26:50,319
[SPEAKER_02] Oh, sto posto.

352
00:26:50,480 --> 00:26:51,119
[SPEAKER_02] Pa, da, da.

353
00:26:51,519 --> 00:26:54,720
[SPEAKER_02] I to je sjajno jer služi kao ta sjeverna zvijezda.

354
00:26:55,680 --> 00:26:58,000
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, bilo je nešto poput pastirskog kaosa u toj ulozi.

355
00:26:58,000 --> 00:27:00,960
